title: Monroe Teasing U Brush
description:
Monroe Teasing U Brush is the perfect brush for teasing or backcombing! 

This excellent quality brush has wood handle with 3 levels of 100% boar bristle. It is extremely efficient and the favorite among stylists!

title: Philosophy Lip Shine, Mimosa, 0.5 Ounce
description: Give your lips a reason to celebrate with mimosa high-gloss, high-flavor lip shine. It hydrates, soothes and softens lips, while providing a beautiful shine.
